data: With this letter, my dear brother, you will receive a part of the manuscripts, which I engaged to send you: these leaves contain the memoirs of the unfortunate Urania Venosta, which have interested me greatly from a variety of reasons.
Feudal tyrants; or, The Counts of Carlsheim and Sargans, volume 2
